section.section:
"Public and commercial building" includes:
Industrial and office buildings;
Residential apartment buildings of 10 or more dwelling units;
Condominiums of 10 or more dwelling units;
Government-owned buildings;
Colleges;
Museums;
Airports;
Hospitals;
Churches;
Stores;
Warehouses; and
Factories.

text.section:
"Public unit" includes:
Any agency, bureau, department, or instrumentality of State government that is not subject to Executive Order 01.01.1987.22;
Any agency, bureau, department, or instrumentality of federal or local government;
Educational institutions that are not subject to Executive Order 01.01.1987.22; and
Any public, quasi-public, or municipal corporation.
